-- Russia c.bank shifts rouble's trading band by 5 kopecks
-- By Lidia Kelly and Alexander Winning
-- Mon Oct 20, 2014 02:08AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Oct 20 (Reuters) - Russia's central bank said on Monday it had shifted the boundaries of its floating rouble corridor by 5 kopecks, following market interventions to curb the pace of the currency's decline.

